     NET    292   0     Net 292   in zone 2  = 0 credits
     NET    512   5     Net 512   in zone 2  = 5 credits

     MYZONE  89         Following definitions are for zone 89
     REGION  12  2      Region 12 in zone 89 = 2 credits
